End block parameters --> \n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h2 class=\"pb-3 mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">ACL Students</h2>\n    <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-light pb-3 mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"></h3>\n    <div mbr-list mbr-list-grow=\"testimonialsItems\" class=\"col-md-10 testimonials-container\"> \n      <div class=\"testimonials-item\">\n        <div class=\"user row\">\n          <div class=\"col-lg-3 col-md-4\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n            <div class=\"user_image\">\n              <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/hung-jin-226x223.jpg\" alt title>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"testimonials-caption\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-9 col-md-8':showImage}\">\n            <div class=\"user_text \">\n              <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".user_text\">Hung-Jin Huang<br>ACL fellow (2019 -)</p><p>I am broadly interested in astrophysical systematics for weak lensing observables. I studied intrinsic alignment in redMaPPer galaxy clusters (Huang et al. 2016, 2018), and investigated mitigation techniques for uncertainties of baryonic physics from hydrodynamical simulations (Huang et al. 2019). I have jointly modeled cosmology and baryonic physics using Dark Energy Survey data (Huang et al 2021).&nbsp;</p><p>I am currently working on a simulation and measurement pipeline for Kinematic Lensing. I am also interested in machine learning applications to increasing the resolution of ground based imaging data using space based observations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div mbr-text class=\"user_name mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style 