bold mbr-fonts-style align-left pt-3\" mbr-if=\"showName\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".user_name\">Paul Rogozenski</div>\n            <div mbr-text class=\"user_desk mbr-light mbr-fonts-style align-left pt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showBiography\" data-app-selector=\".user_desk\">Graduate Student in Physics (Advisor: Elisabeth Krause)</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
